{"arkId":"cl010112463","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010112463","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre astronomique","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre astronomique"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Henri IV (1589-1610) (Occident-\u003ERenaissance-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons) ; Louis XIII (1610-1643) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1600 - 1650","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 4","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1600,"endYear":1650,"imprecision":"","text":"1ere moiti\u00e9 du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Silleman, Joost","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 7073","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre astronomique ; bo\u00eetier circulaire en cristal de roche biseaut\u00e9 et taill\u00e9 sur ses deux faces de douze lobes convergeant vers une creusure. Armatures grav\u00e9es de rinceaux peupl\u00e9s d\u0027animaux courant. Pendant en forme de chapiteau et bouton moulur\u00e9. Au centre du cadran, disque grav\u00e9 de figures g\u00e9om\u00e9triques d\u00e9terminant l\u0027influence de la position des astres ; ouverture d\u00e9voilant la phase de la lune. Cercle num\u00e9rot\u00e9e de 1 \u00e0 30 indiquant l\u0027\u00e2ge de la lune ; un second marque les quanti\u00e8mes. Heures indiqu\u00e9e en chiffres romains. Echappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre, fus\u00e9e avec corde \u00e0 boyau. Coq et cliquet reperc\u00e9s et grav\u00e9s de rinceaux \u00e0 fleurs de fraisier.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : J Silleman fec\/Leward\u00e9","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"5","displayDimension":"5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"3,5","displayDimension":"3,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"1","displayDimension":"1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : cristal de roche\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"Leeuwarden (Europe-\u003EPays-Bas = Pays Bas = Hollande)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Paul Garnier (1834-1916), \u00e0 Paris. Don Paul Garnier, en 1916.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Garnier, Paul ","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1916","startYear":1916,"endYear":1916}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"period":[{"value":"Henri IV (1589-1610)"},{"value":"Louis XIII (1610-1643)"}],"place":[{"value":"Leeuwarden"}],"objectType":[{"value":"horlogerie"},{"value":"montre"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Cardinal, Catherine, Les montres et horloges de table du mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Tome 2, Paris, RMN, 2000","bibliographyDate":"2000","bibliographyDetail":"n\u00b0 131","comparison":false}],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louv